      *
      * Transaction file to be processed
      *
     F***********DEALS   IF  E           K        DISK                    CSD004
     FDEALSL2 IF  E           K        DISK                               CSD004
     F            DEALSDAF                          KIGNORE
     F            DEALSDBF                          KIGNORE
     F            DEALSDDF                          KIGNORE
     F            DEALSDEF                          KIGNORE
     F            DEALSDFF                          KIGNORE
     F            DEALSDGF                          KIGNORE
