      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * Program Initiation Processing:                                *
      *                                                               *
      * Sets up the copyright statement.                              *
      * Obtains rundate.                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** Define LDA
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      BIS@   80
      *
      ** Obtain rundate from SDBANKPD
      *
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST ' BANKOP  7
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   BANKRC  7        Return code
     C                     PARM           BANKOP           Option
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    @FMT             Format
      *
      ** Check for error in SDBANKPD
      *
     C           BANKRC    IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD001       DBASE
     C                     MOVEL'SD4104'  DBPGM            **************
     C                     MOVEL'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 001*
     C                     MOVEL'BANK'    DBKEY            **************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     END
      *
      ** Save today's date
      *
     C                     Z-ADDBJRDNB    RUNDAT  50
      *
      ** Initialise the live and inserted record counters
      *
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    IPTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    IPTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    TITTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    TITTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    CLTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    CLTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    ITTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    ITTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    TDTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    TDTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    CDTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    CDTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    CITTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    CITTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    ILTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    ILTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTLV    IDTTLV
     C           *LIKE     DEFN E0TTIN    IDTTIN
     C           *LIKE     DEFN BRCA      UCBRCA                          CSD004
     C                     MOVEL*HIVAL    UCBRCA                          CSD004
      *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * Program Main Processing:                                      *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** Read Transaction File until EOF
      ** DEALS contains live records only
      *
     C           *IN01     DOUEQ'1'
     C***********          READ DEALS                  0101               CSD004
     C                     READ DEALSL2                0101               CSD004
      *
      ** If record found - include it in today's count
      *
     C           *IN01     IFEQ '0'
      ** First time                                                       CSD004
      *                                                                   CSD004
     C           UCBRCA    IFEQ *HIVAL                                    CSD004
     C                     MOVELBRCA      UCBRCA                          CSD004
     C                     ENDIF                                          CSD004
      *                                                                   CSD004
      ** On each break down on branch - output totals to                  CSD004
      ** SDBTMMPD                                                         CSD004
     C           BRCA      IFNE UCBRCA                                    CSD004
     C                     MOVE UCBRCA    @DSNB                           CSD004
     C                     EXSR RVBRCA                                    CSD004
     C                     EXSR OUTPUT                                    CSD004
     C                     MOVELBRCA      UCBRCA                          CSD004
     C                     ENDIF                                          CSD004
      *
     C           RECI      IFEQ 'D'
     C                     EXSR COUNT
     C                     ENDIF
     C           RECI      IFEQ 'M'
     C           ORED      ANDEQRUNDAT
     C                     EXSR COUNT
     C                     ENDIF
      *                                                                   CSD004
     C                     ELSE                                           CSD004
      *                                                                   CSD004
      *                                                                   CSD004
      ** End of the file / DEALSL2                                        CSD004
      ** At least one record found                                        CSD004
     C           UCBRCA    IFNE *HIVAL                                    CSD004
     C                     MOVE BRCA      @DSNB                           CSD004
     C                     EXSR RVBRCA                                    CSD004
     C                     ENDIF                                          CSD004
      *
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *                                                                   CSD004
      *
      ***When*all*records*have*been*processed*-*output*totals*to*******   CSD004
      ***SDBTMMPD**********************************                       CSD004
      *
     C           UCBRCA    IFNE *HIVAL                                    CSD004
     C                     EXSR OUTPUT
     C                     ENDIF                                          CSD004
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * COUNT  - Calculates today's totals ready for output.          *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: Main processing                                    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           COUNT     BEGSR
      *
      ** Deal type 'IP' - Interbank Deposit Placed
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'IP'
     C                     ADD  1         IPTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         IPTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal type 'TI' - Time Deposit Placed
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'TI'
     C                     ADD  1         TITTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         TITTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal type 'CL' - Call Notice Deposit Placed
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'CL'
     C                     ADD  1         CLTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         CLTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'IT' - Interbank Deposit Taken
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'IT'
     C                     ADD  1         ITTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         ITTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'TD' - Time Deposit Accepted
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'TD'
     C                     ADD  1         TDTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         TDTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'CD' - Call Notice Deposit/Taken
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'CD'
     C                     ADD  1         CDTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         CDTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'CI' - Certificate of Deposit Issued
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'CI'
     C                     ADD  1         CITTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         CITTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'IL' - Internal Loans
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'IL'
     C                     ADD  1         ILTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         ILTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      ** Deal types 'ID' - Internal Loans
      ** increase the live record counter by 1
      *
     C           DTYP      IFEQ 'ID'
     C                     ADD  1         IDTTLV
      *
      ** If the deal was placed in the system today then
      ** increase the inserted record counter by 1
      *
     C           ORED      IFEQ RUNDAT
     C                     ADD  1         IDTTIN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     END
      *
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * OUTPUT - Outputs today's totals to SDBTMMPD.                  *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: Main processing                                    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           OUTPUT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Move Transaction File name, Transaction File module
      ** and Midas run date into SDBTMMPD fields ready for output
      *
     C                     MOVEL'DEALSDC' E0FNME
     C                     MOVEL'MM'      E0MMOD
     C                     Z-ADDBJRDNB    E0DATE
      *
      ** Move branch and company codes                                    CSD004
      *                                                                   CSD004
     C                     MOVE A8BRCD    E0BRCA                          CSD004
     C                     MOVE A8CMCD    E0CMPY                          CSD004
      *
      ** Output processing for Deal Type 'IP' - Interbank Deposit
      *                                         Placed
      *
      ** Move Deal Type, total inserts today and total
      ** live records into SDBTMMPD fields ready for output
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   E0TNTY
     C                     MOVE 'IP'      E0TNTY
     C                     Z-ADDIPTTIN    E0TTIN
     C                     Z-ADDIPTTLV    E0TTLV
      *
      ** Write a record to SDBTMMPD
      *
     C                     WRITESDBTSMD0
      *
