     C                     Z-ADDIDTTLV    E0TTLV
      *
      ** Write a record to SDBTMMPD
      *
     C                     WRITESDBTSMD0
      *
      ***When*all*Deal*Type*records*have*been*written*to***************   CSD004
      ***SDBTMMPD*-*end*program*normally*************                     CSD004
      *
      *  Reset the count variables for the next branch                    CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         IPTTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         IPTTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         TITTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         TITTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CLTTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CLTTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         ITTTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         ITTTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         TDTTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         TDTTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CDTTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CDTTIN                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CITTLV                          CSD004
     C                     Z-ADD0         CITTIN                          CSD004
